      "Artie has 1 HP and 1 MP; any damage taken is lethal due to rounding rules.",
      "Artie has 100% Critical Hit rate.",
      "The Super-Mega-Ultra-Crit has a 24-hour cooldown."
    ]
  },
  "world_updates": {
    "cast_present": [
