      "Artie reached Level 2 and received a Dexterity pity bonus.",
      "The Whispering Woods now contains a fifty-foot furrow and a smoking crater.",
      "Artie's Super-Mega-Ultra-Crit has entered a 24-hour cooldown."
    ]
  }
}

